116
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:31,120
- Chết tiệt.
- Thằng chó này.

117
00:10:31,190 --> 00:10:33,390
- Chết tiệt.
- Thằng chó.

118
00:10:33,490 --> 00:10:34,550
